## 7.2 Vector Store (Pinecone)

* **Provider**: Pinecone (Serverless)
* **Model**: `llama-text-embed-v2` (NVIDIA – Hosted)
* **Type**: Dense Vector
* **Limits**: 5M tokens (Free Tier)
* **Integration**: Integrated Inference (Pinecone handles embedding generation)
* **Index**: `medications` namespace
* **Fields**: `text` (embedded), `brand_name`, `generic_name` (metadata)

