# 14. Non-functional metrics to track (MVP)

* **End-to-end latency** (STT→response): target < 2.5s.
* **Parsing accuracy** (manual test set): target > 90% for top-200 meds.
* **Vector match accuracy**: top-1 match > 0.75 similarity on test phrases.
* **Autonomy ratio**: percent of flows that complete without manual admin intervention (target > 70% for in-catalog flows).
* **Intervention count**: number of times demo operator must intervene (target ≤ 1 per demo flow).

