# 21. Acceptance Criteria (how we win)

* Live demo shows: voice input → agent resolves intent → UI shows in-stock options → agent enforces RX check → item added to cart — within ≤ 2.5s E2E for typical queries.
* Agent trace is visible and explains each step.
* Admin can add or edit meds during demo and changes are reflected immediately.
* Substitutions only suggested for same active ingredient and only if in-stock.
* No hallucinated advice, no autosubstitution across classes, no recommending antibiotics.

